{"tid":925740,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華明邨20歲女子墮樓重傷送院","createTime":"2018-12-03T03:14:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-03T03:14:10.000Z","uid":160807,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ec7c2c300f5a49d5f94c36f87048608ff4195f07","tid":925740,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T03:14:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181203/photo/bkn-20181203091436302-1203_00822_001_03b.jpg?20181203111235\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181203%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181203091436302-1203_00822_001_03b.jpg%3F20181203111235&h=57a34e58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n粉嶺華明邨富明樓一單位，今早(3日)8時45分，一名20餘歲女子被發現危坐窗邊，警方及消防員趕至時，女子已由高處墮下重傷，救護員在現場為女子急救後送院，警方正調查她墮樓原因。<br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線：<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222<br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000<br />\n明愛向晴軒： 18288<br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000<br />\n東華三院芷若園： 18281<br />\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350<br />\n利民會： 3512 2626<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=T4XM9PkblQOSe8zhi732TcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=fd119fa7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181203/bkn-20181203091436302-1203_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181203%2Fbkn-20181203091436302-1203_00822_001.html&d=T4XM9PkblQOSe8zhi732TcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=b34470c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181203/bkn-20181203091436302-1203_00822_001.html</a>"}]}